{"tid":1036454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雷斯：我叫Kepa尊重領隊","createTime":"2019-02-25T08:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T12:06:02.000Z","uid":5649,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"43bb0333223e63235793e573befc7c9aa3fd9502","tid":1036454,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8QzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=7944937a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】車路士門將阿列沙巴拿加跟領隊沙利，於周日英聯盃決賽爆出拒絕被換的風波，中堅大衛雷斯透露，當時曾勸前者要尊重主帥。<br />\n<br />\n正當阿列沙巴拿加在龍門前，遠距離跟於場邊的沙利「開火」時，大衛雷斯（David Luiz）是最接近Kepa的球員，亦是唯一一名走上前安撫對方的隊友。<br />\n<br />\n雷斯賽後表示：「我只是跟Kepa說，我們要尊重領隊的決定。我不知道領隊希望換走Kepa，是因為他感到痛楚，還是戰術原因；我猜領隊不肯定他的傷勢如何，Kepa卻不明白。」<br />\n<br />\n這名巴西國腳續指，Kepa跟他表示傷患沒有大礙：「在比賽期間，有時候你沒有太多時間去解釋事情，這是很正常的事。」<br />\n<br />\nKepa最終未有被換走，更在互射12碼撲出1球，可惜車路士有中場佐真奴費路射失、雷斯射中柱，以3:4不敵曼城，飲恨僅得亞軍。"},{"pid":"5683f1658293bce1ad8437f2f59a5f2451afc502","tid":1036454,"uid":70195,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"邊個有份射失12碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5af20eef2affed7f281ded02f6b8a40681dcde5","tid":1036454,"uid":27851,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"果然係世一龍 大牌到🤙🏻🤙🏻skr"},{"pid":"2ecb99509cdadae8877901133cdd974a67a2c93b","tid":1036454,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5683f1658293bce1ad8437f2f59a5f2451afc502","tid":1036454,"uid":70195,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"邊個有份射失12碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"Sane<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620c7f28781944a1d1f9a415d6e741aa3fd8c8e7","tid":1036454,"uid":74185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p